# ── PCR-024: agent-answer noise files (2026-06-08) ────────────────────────
# Some agent endpoint writes its "answers" to disk at unpredictable paths.
# On 2026-06-08 01:18 UTC this gutted src/executor_agent.py (restored at
# 23:09 UTC). On 2026-06-08 ~23:00 UTC inspection found 22 shadow files
# inside src/ that would import-shadow real modules — quarantined into
# /var/lib/murphy-production/state_snapshots/shadow_quarantine/.
# This block stops the noise from polluting commits while the underlying
# write-endpoint audit remains banked for a future session.

# Root-level agent answer dumps
/answer.txt
